message:
If you guys have some last minute Christmas 🎄 shopping to do come stop by our Entrepreneurship Holiday Market at Rapson hall courtyard this Thursday December 8th from 9:00 am - 11:00 am !! 

There are lots of products for sale hand made by U of M students 〽️ such as wine racks 🍷, Minnesota shirts, bath bombs, soaps, room decor, skyline business cards, coffee bags 👜, and many more gifts for sale!
